    <note>Wang(2) Yi(3) [7082] Anshi's [1762], Anguo's [7076], Anli's [1760] and Anshang's [1761] father, Fang's [1803] and Fu(2)'s [1805] grandfather, Guan's [1841] nephew, Wu(3) Tian's [7396] son-in-law, father-in-law of Zhu(1) Mingzhi [526], Shen(2) Jichang [1445] and of Zhang(1) Ruogu's [245] son, Kui [3150]. Yi(3) was Gong(2) Yuan's [941] maternal grandfather and his granddaughter was betrothed to Wu(3) Anchi [1957]. He was a tongnianyou of Chen(1) Jiansu [7102]. Zeng Gong, WJ, 44.6a-7b, 45.4b-6a (wife, born Wu, who died in 1063 at age 66); Wang Anshi, WJ, 71.750-1. CBD, 1, 148-9.</note>
